These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different games are played: go, monopoly, poker
1. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the person playing poker is between the person playing go and the person playing monopoly##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Game   | go | poker | monopoly |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, subway
1. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the subway##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Transport   | subway | jet-ski | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different nationalities: french, thai, spanish
1. the thai is between the french and the spanish##2
2. the thai is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Nationality   | spanish | thai | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, action, time-travel
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching action movies and the person watching adventure movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | time-travel | action |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Hobby   | card-games | board-games | sudoku |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, august, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in february##2
2. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2    |      3      |
| Birthday   | august | october | february |

 #################################

 
